---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout 
  title="Privacy Policy | Mountos codeLab"
  description="Our data protocol."
>
  <div class="static-page">
    <h1>[ Privacy_Protocol ]</h1>
    <div class="content">
      <p>
        &gt; System log started. This document outlines the data protocol for this node (mountos.codelab).
      </p>
      
      <h2>// Data Footprint</h2>
      <p>
        &gt; We run a minimal operation. We do not require user registration. We do not actively collect personal data. Your IP address and user agent may be logged by the server for security and diagnostic purposes. This is standard procedure.
      </p>

      <h2>// Cookies_&_Trackers</h2>
      <p>
        &gt; This site is static. We do not use cookies for tracking or advertising. If any client-side scripts are active, they are for functionality (e.g., search) and not for surveillance. We have no interest in your browsing history.
      </p>

      <h2>// Third-Party_Comms</h2>
      <p>
        &gt; We do not share data with third parties. There is no data to share. All processing is done on-node or on your local client.
      </p>

      <h2>// Protocol_Updates</h2>
      <p>
        &gt; This protocol is subject to change without notice. We are not a corporation. We are a lab. Assume nothing.
      </p>

      <h2>// End_of_Transmission</h2>
      <p>
        &gt; Questions can be sent to `/dev/null`.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>

<style>
  .static-page {
    max-width: 720px;
    margin: auto;
  }
  .static-page h1 {
    font-size: 2.8rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    text-align: center;
    text-shadow: 0 0 8px var(--color-text);
  }
  .content {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
  }
  .content h2 {
    font-size: 1.8rem;
		margin-top: 3rem;
		margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
		line-height: 1.3;
		border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border);
		padding-bottom: .5rem;
    text-shadow: 0 0 5px var(--color-text);
  }
  .content p {
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
</style>